No. 10-1059. Yankton Sioux Tribe, et al., Petitioners v. United States Army Corps of Engineers, et al. 564 U.S. 1030, 131 S. Ct. 3026,

180 L. Ed. 2d 865,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4638. June 20, 2011.

Motion of Southern Missouri Recycling and Waste Management District for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 606 F.3d 895.
